        <div class="track-card-desc">Are you getting stronger, holding steady, or gradually declining? Strength trend is a more honest proxy for muscle health than any scale number.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="track-card">
        <div class="track-card-num">03</div>
        <div class="track-card-title">Body composition</div>
        <div class="track-card-desc">If you have access to a DEXA scan or body composition assessment, the muscle-to-fat ratio tells you far more than BMI. Not essential, but more meaningful.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="track-card">
